  ],
  "remarks": "JSC STC Promtekhaero (a.k.a. Scientific and Technical Center for Industrial Technologies and Air Navigation Systems) is a Russian military-industrial state enterprise that develops radio transmission and navigation equipment deployed by the Russian armed forces. Moreover, JSC STC Promtekhaero is part of the Joint Stock Company Almaz-Antey air and space defence corporation, a Russian state-owned arms manufacturer that develops anti-aircraft defence and cruise missile systems for the Russian military.",
